snippet.title: Undertale Tag - Fangame Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Undertale Tag is fully releasing Late February! Download on Gamejolt when it releases: https://gamejolt.com/games/UnderTag/449425
Undertale Tag is an Undertale fangame in where two humans fall into the Underground, but only Frisk has a SOUL.

Undertale Tag's main gimmick is the tag ability. This ability allows the player to swap control between the two humans. Solve puzzles that require teamwork, on your own.This is an Undertale fangame, so will you slay every monster that crosses your path? Or maybe you'll show some mercy? With four official endings to the game, the choice is yours. This new underground will go empty, but in what way?
